					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5779856#post-3813353</guid>
				<title>I like every part of this.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5779856/scp-3716#post-3813353</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 26 May 2018 03:45:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mark Simmons</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2988223</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The less-than-enormous stakes, the idea of a Foundation-made GoI, the general silliness of the Brotherhood of Spooky Scary Skeletons, how it hints at how the situation might end up out of control, but doesn’t shove your face in it, all of it. +1 for a good laugh.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
