					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5779856#post-3782991</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5779856/scp-3716#post-3782991</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 27 Apr 2018 19:18:44 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>2303803</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It sure is refreshing to see a group affiliated with the anomalous or directly involving the anomalous being somewhat amicable toward the Foundation, even if the Foundation is having to contain their shit. I actually think it's more realistic than the usual narrative pattern of pitting them against each other and/or making everything the Foundation is doing nonconsensual. Leaves more room to focus on what's going on in the setting.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
